`0Help for the Read Ads Menu ------------------

<F> Read Forward    - Read ads in forward order starting with a
                      specified message number.
<R> Read Reverse    - Read ads in reverse order starting with a
                      specified message number.
<I> Read Individual - Read an individual message.  If you choose this
                      option, you will be prompted for which message
                      number to read.
<S> Read Search     - Read ads in the fields:  To name, From name,
                      or Subject.  You will be prompted which field you want to
                      search on.
<X> Exit            - Exit to the previous menu.

Press ENTER to continue....`4
